overrideValues.value: After the Filter buton has been pressed / clicked an accordian dropdown is exposed to reveal filtering options

- Bread Crumbs remain
- Search field remains
- Filter button text is rendered as "close" and should close the filter on click / press
- Filter Results heading appears
- Filter by Format, Date and Language options are rendered where available
- Apply Filter button appears to set chosen filters
- Clear filters button appears
- Number of results per page remains
- Sort by relevance button remains
- After filters are set, apply button should set filters and close the drop down, exposing the new set of results
